WEAR - Put on armor
===================

Usage: wear <armor>

Equips a piece of armor from your inventory. Armor reduces damage taken
in combat.

Examples:
  wear cap
  wear pelt
  wear gloves

Notes:
  - Each armor piece goes in a specific slot (head, torso, hands, etc.)
  - You can only wear one item per slot
  - Total armor is the sum of all equipped pieces
  - Damage taken = incoming damage - total armor (minimum 1)

See also: help remove, help equipment, help combat
